---
import DocsLayout from '../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="配置参考" description="PicFast 完整配置参考。">
  <h1>配置参考</h1>
  <p>PicFast 通过 <code>config.yaml</code> 或环境变量进行配置。</p>

  <h2>完整示例</h2>
  <pre><code>server:
  port: 8080
  base_url: "https://pics.example.com"
  web_dir: ""
  pprof_enabled: false

database:
  url: "postgres://picfast:picfast@localhost:5432/picfast?sslmode=disable"

jwt:
  secret: "change-me-in-production"
  access_ttl: "15m"
  refresh_ttl: "168h"
  signing_method: "HS256"

storage:
  local_root: "./data/uploads"
  thumbnail_dir: "./data/thumbnails"

mail:
  host: "smtp.example.com"
  port: 587
  username: ""
  password: ""
  from_email: ""
  from_name: "PicFast"
  encryption: "starttls"

app:
  name: "PicFast"
  site_description: "我的图床服务"
  allow_guest_upload: false
  allow_registration: true
  require_email_verification: false
  audit_upload_logs: true
  user_initial_capacity: 524288000
  default_image_ttl: ""
  admin_email: "admin@example.com"
  admin_password: "changeme"
  moderation_mode: ""
  icp_number: ""
  icp_link: "https://beian.miit.gov.cn/"
  psb_number: ""
  psb_link: ""</code></pre>

  <h2>配置项说明</h2>

  <h3>server</h3>
  <table>
    <thead><tr><th>键</th><th>类型</th><th>默认值</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>port</code></td><td>int</td><td>8080</td><td>监听端口</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>base_url</code></td><td>string</td><td>http://localhost:8080</td><td>服务公开访问地址</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>web_dir</code></td><td>string</td><td>""</td><td>前端文件目录（可选）</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>pprof_enabled</code></td><td>bool</td><td>false</td><td>开启 Go pprof 端点（仅管理员）</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h3>jwt</h3>
  <table>
    <thead><tr><th>键</th><th>类型</th><th>默认值</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>secret</code></td><td>string</td><td>—</td><td><strong>必填。</strong> Token 签名密钥，必须修改。</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>access_ttl</code></td><td>duration</td><td>15m</td><td>Access token 有效期</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>refresh_ttl</code></td><td>duration</td><td>168h</td><td>Refresh token 有效期（7 天）</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>signing_method</code></td><td>string</td><td>HS256</td><td>HS256、HS384 或 HS512</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h3>app</h3>
  <table>
    <thead><tr><th>键</th><th>类型</th><th>默认值</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>allow_guest_upload</code></td><td>bool</td><td>false</td><td>允许不登录上传</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>allow_registration</code></td><td>bool</td><td>false</td><td>允许新用户注册</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>require_email_verification</code></td><td>bool</td><td>false</td><td>登录前必须验证邮箱</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>audit_upload_logs</code></td><td>bool</td><td>false</td><td>记录所有上传操作日志</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>user_initial_capacity</code></td><td>bytes</td><td>524288000</td><td>新用户默认存储配额（500 MB）</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>default_image_ttl</code></td><td>duration</td><td>""</td><td>图片默认过期时间（空=永不过期）</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>moderation_mode</code></td><td>string</td><td>""</td><td><code>disabled</code>、<code>manual</code> 或 <code>auto</code></td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</DocsLayout>
